The mission is NOT terminated — it delivered this result and is now parked in `awaiting_dismissal`, awaiting your next directive. To continue the same thread call `session:notify_subagent({subagent_id: "{{.MissionID}}", content: "<your directive>"})` — its working context (notepad cache, prior introspection) is still alive. To tear it down — when the work is final or your next user message is unrelated — call `session:subagent_dismiss({session_id: "{{.MissionID}}"})`. Leaving it parked occupies a slot on the per-root cap; be intentional.
{{end}}
Use `session:subagent_runs({{.MissionID}})` for full details.
